    <td style="padding-top:0.01in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:4.3pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><span style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Date:</span></p></td>
    <td style="padding-top:0.01in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:4.3pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><span style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">February 27, 2025</span></p></td>
    <td style="padding-top:0.01in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:4.3pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><span style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">By:</span><span style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </span></p></td>
    <td style="padding-top:0.01in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;border-bottom:0.25pt solid;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:4.3pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><span style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">/s/ Elizabeth O'Callahan</span></p></td>
   </tr>
   <tr style="height:10pt;white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-word;">

    <td style="padding-top:0.01in;vertical-align:top;padding-bottom:0in;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><span style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</span></p></td>

 <body style="padding:8px;margin:auto!important;">
  <div style="padding-top:0.5in;z-index:-3;min-height:0.38in;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div>
  <p style="margin-left:10%;text-indent:3.704%;font-size:10pt;margin-top:6pt;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:right;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Exhibit 99.1</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:center;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:center;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp Reports Third Quarter of Fiscal Year 2025 Results</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.796%;text-align:center;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Net revenues of $1.64 billion for the third quarter</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">All-flash array annualized net revenue run rate</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">1</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> of $3.8 billion, an increase of 10% year-over-year</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">First-party and marketplace cloud storage services revenue again grew more than 40% year-over-year</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Continued to deliver significant intelligent data infrastructure innovation with the launch of new all-flash NetApp</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#153; </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">AFF A-Series and C-Series systems, enhanced StorageGRID</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#153;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> object storage capabilities, and expanded cloud storage offerings</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Third quarter GAAP operating margin of 22%; third quarter non-GAAP operating margin</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">2</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> of 30%</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Third quarter GAAP net income per share</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">3</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> of $1.44; third quarter non-GAAP net income per share</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">2</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> of $1.91</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Returned $306 million to stockholders through share repurchases and cash dividends</font></div></div>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">SAN JOSE, Calif.&#x2014;February 27, 2025&#x2014;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp (NASDAQ: NTAP), the intelligent data infrastructure company, today reported financial results for the third quarter of fiscal year 2025, which ended on January 24, 2025.</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#x201c;The strength of our business model yielded operating margin ahead of and EPS in-line with expectations, despite Q3 top line performance below our standards,&#x201d; said George Kurian, chief executive officer. &#x201c;We are taking action to enhance our execution and improve our momentum. I remain confident in our position as the supplier of choice for AI and other data-driven workloads and our ability to achieve our long-term financial goals and deliver increasing shareholder value. Our portfolio has never been stronger, delivering a modern approach to hybrid, multicloud infrastructure and data management and giving customers the ability to leverage the power of their entire data estate simply, securely, and sustainably.&#x201d;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:-1.709%;padding-left:1.667%;font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Third Quarter of Fiscal Year 2025 Financial Results</font></p>
  <p style="text-indent:-1.709%;padding-left:1.667%;font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Net revenues:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> $1.64 billion, compared to $1.61 billion in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024; a year-over-year increase of 2%.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="margin-left:2.667%;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.9181572539631986%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">o</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Hybrid Cloud segment revenue:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> $1.47 billion, compared to $1.46 billion in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="margin-left:2.667%;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.9181572539631986%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">o</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Public Cloud segment revenue:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> $174 million, compared to $151 million in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Billings</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">2</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">: </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">$1.71 billion, compared to $1.69 billion in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024; a year-over-year increase of 2%. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">All-flash array ARR: </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">$3.8 billion, compared to $3.4 billion in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024; a year-over-year increase of 10%.</font></div></div>
  <div class="page-border-spacing"><div style="z-index:-3;flex-direction:column;display:flex;padding-bottom:0.5in;min-height:0.5in;justify-content:flex-end;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div></div>
  <hr style="margin-inline-start:auto;margin-inline-end:auto;page-break-after:always;">
  <div style="padding-top:0.5in;z-index:-3;min-height:0.38in;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Net income:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> GAAP net income of $299 million, compared to $313 million in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024; non-GAAP net income</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">of $397 million, compared to $410 million in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Earnings per share:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> GAAP net income per share</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">of $1.44, compared to $1.48 in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024; non-GAAP net income per share of $1.91, compared to $1.94 in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Cash, cash equivalents and investments:</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> $2.26 billion at the end of the third quarter of fiscal year 2025.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Cash provided by operations: </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">$385 million, compared to $484 million in the third quarter of fiscal year 2024.</font></div></div>

  <div style="padding-top:0.5in;z-index:-3;min-height:0.38in;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp introduced additional high-performance, unified data storage </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">AFF A-Series </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">entry and midrange platforms, which deliver advanced features for mission-critical workloads at affordable price points. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp introduced new </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">AFF C-Series</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> systems aimed at providing greater value for general-purpose workloads and consolidating workloads across unified file, block, and object storage protocols while delivering industry-leading density and efficiency. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp extended the </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">StorageGRID SFG6112</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> system with support 60TB capacity flash drives, doubling the density of object deployments, reducing rack space, and lowering power and cooling costs. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp updated </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">StorageGRID</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> software with improved scalability and flexibility for increased performance with small object workloads and mixed-media grids. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp expanded the </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">E-Series product family with the E4000 systems</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, providing simple high-performance SAN storage for backup, video surveillance, HPC, and AI-driven applications. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp announced the </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">general availability of NetApp Trident&#153; 24.10 software</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, enabling Kubernetes workloads to benefit from the scale, performance, availability, and advanced data protection features of NetApp ONTAP technology for both on-premises and cloud environments.</font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp BlueXP&#153;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> adds ransomware integration with </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Microsoft Sentinel</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> and new workload management features. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp continues to simplify data estate operations by enabling automated </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">ONTAP and anti-ransomware</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">updates through</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">BlueXP</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">.</font></div></div>

  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">The San Francisco 49ers</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> and NetApp announced a </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">multiyear strategic partnership</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, designating NetApp as the </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Official Intelligent Data Infrastructure Partner</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">. The partnership is helping the 49ers leverage intelligent data infrastructure to enhance business operations, beginning with a </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">reimagined fan experience at Levi&#x2019;s Stadium</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp and Red Hat expanded their partnership to </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">integrate NetApp&#x2019;s intelligent data infrastructure with Red Hat OpenShift</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, enhancing flexibility for managing virtualized environments across on-premises and hybrid multicloud. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp introduced </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">on-premises enterprise storage arrays for AWS Outposts</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, enabling customers to manage external block data volumes directly through the AWS Management Console. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp announced that </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Amazon FSx for NetApp ONTAP</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;vertical-align:super;font-size:7.37pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#153;</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> was </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">certified for Siemens Teamcenter on</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">AWS</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, bringing enhanced performance, scalability, and data management capabilities to product lifecycle management workloads in the cloud. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Microsoft Azure</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> introduced</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> Azure NetApp Files cool access support for large volumes</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, which significantly improves the effective price of storage by moving infrequently accessed data to a lower-cost tier. </font></div></div>

  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp announced the availability of </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp Data Infrastructure Insights on the Azure Marketplace</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, offering streamlined infrastructure observability, automation, and real-time telemetry data to customers migrating to Azure. </font></div></div>

  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp announced it had entered into an agreement for the </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">sale of its Spot by NetApp</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">FinOps business to</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">Flexera</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, reflecting NetApp&#x2019;s focus and commitment to intelligent data infrastructure and long-term growth opportunities. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp announced that it approved new near-term science-based </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">emissions reduction targets verified by the Science-Based Targets initiative (SBTi),</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> demonstrating the company&#x2019;s commitment to making sustainability a crucial component of its business resilience strategy. </font></div></div>

  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp was named one of the </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">20 Coolest Cloud Storage Companies</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> as part of </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">CRN</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#x2019;s 2025 Cloud 100 awards</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">, highlighting the company&#x2019;s silo-free approach to storage, which combines unified data storage with enterprise-grade storage services natively embedded in the top cloud hyperscalers. </font></div></div>
  <div class="item-list-element-wrapper" style="display:flex;margin-top:6pt;justify-content:flex-start;align-items:baseline;margin-bottom:0;min-width:1.333%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:1.333%;word-break:keep-all;display:inline-flex;justify-content:flex-start;">&#x2022;</font><div style="width:100%;display:inline;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-style:italic;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">CRN </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">named</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> NetApp Senior GMT Program Manager Monica Scaglia</font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> to its </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">2024 Channel Women on the Rise </font><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">list.</font></div></div>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-weight:bold;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>

  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">This press release contains forward-looking statements within the meaning of the Private Securities Litigation Reform Act of 1995. These statements include, but are not limited to, all of the statements made in the Fourth Quarter of Fiscal Year 2025 Financial Outlook section and the Full Fiscal Year 2025 Financial Outlook section, and statements about our business, economic and market outlook, financial guidance, our overall future prospects, our ability to compete for AI and other data-driven workloads against our competitors, our ability to deliver a modern approach to hybrid, multicloud infrastructure and data management, and our ability to deliver increasing results and value for our stakeholders. Actual results may differ materially from these statements for a variety of reasons, including, without limitation, our ability to keep pace with the rapid industry, technological and market trends and changes in the markets in which we operate; our ability to execute our evolved cloud strategy and introduce and gain market acceptance for our products and services; our ability to maintain our customer, partner, supplier and contract manufacturer relationships on favorable terms and conditions; global political, macroeconomic and market conditions, including inflation, fluctuating interest rates, tariffs, changes in trade policy, regulations, monetary policy shifts, recession risks, and foreign exchange volatility and the resulting impact on demand for our products; the impact of new or ongoing geopolitical conflicts and sanctions; adoption or changes to laws, regulations standards or policies affecting our operations, products, services, the storage industry, or AI usage; material cybersecurity and other security breaches; the impact of supply chain disruptions on our business operations, financial performance and results of operations; changes and related uncertainty in U.S. government spending or policy; changes in overall technology spending by our customers; revenue seasonality; changes in laws or regulations, including those relating to privacy, data protection and information security; the timing of orders and their fulfilment; and our ability to manage our gross profit margins, including managing component costs. These and other equally important factors are described in reports and documents we file from time to time with the Securities and Exchange Commission, including the factors described under the sections titled &#x201c;Risk Factors&#x201d; in our most recently filed annual report on Form 10-K and quarterly report on Form 10-Q. We disclaim any obligation to update information contained in this press release whether as a result of new information, future events, or otherwise.</font></p>

  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;"> </font></p>
  <div class="page-border-spacing"><div style="z-index:-3;flex-direction:column;display:flex;padding-bottom:0.5in;min-height:0.5in;justify-content:flex-end;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div></div>

  <div style="padding-top:0.5in;z-index:-3;min-height:0.38in;position:relative;box-sizing:border-box;"><p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;text-align:left;"><font style="white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:10pt;font-family:Times New Roman;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">&#160;</font></p></div>
  <p style="font-size:10pt;margin-top:0;font-family:Times New Roman;margin-bottom:0;margin-right:0.833%;text-align:left;"><font style="color:#000000;white-space:pre-wrap;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;font-kerning:none;min-width:fit-content;">NetApp, the NetApp logo, and the marks listed at http://www.netapp.com/TM are trademarks of NetApp, Inc.
